          “The ICT hub environment was perfect for learning and networking with other tech professionals.”
        </p>
        <h4 class="text-brand-gold font-bold text-lg">Kemi Ade</h4>
        <p class="text-white/60 text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">ICT Hub</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 text-left">
        <div class="text-brand-gold text-sm mb-4">★★★★☆</div>
        <p class="text-white italic leading-relaxed mb-4">
          “The academy instructors explained complex concepts clearly. Highly recommended for anyone learning tech.”
        </p>
        <h4 class="text-brand-gold font-bold text-lg">Joshua Eze</h4>
